e/Kei_Nishikori\"}, {\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.49845743087573e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the former world No.\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 prepares to hang up his racket in Paris, he is hoping that he can go out on a high as he addressed his partnership with Evans.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999054126, \"rank\": 9.452092612842334e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.999834768672374, \"rank\": 0.00016525863315581003, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray breezed past Nishikori in the singles semi-final at Rio 2016 en route to his second gold medal.\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 514, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.49845743087573e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when they meet at Stade Roland Garros, it will be a completely different situation.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both men are now in the twilight of their careers after years of injury woes.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, they will face off in the first round of the men's doubles.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Murray knows that the Japanese team could cause them some trouble.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.49845743087573e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9951556594462955, \"rank\": 0.004739534530359551, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They will not have played too much doubles together over the years.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Kei is obviously a classy tennis player, he has played a lot of doubles over the years and can play very well.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keiko_Masuda\", \"score\": 0.9579922070822791, \"rank\": 0.02286934064589767, \"text\": \"Kei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keiko_Masuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keiko_Masuda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have played Daniel in singles, I lost to him at the Australian Open a few years ago,\\\" he said after learning his fate.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Novak Djokovic and Rafael Nadal in line for mammoth early Olympics clash  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    The three-time Grand Slam champion is still confident in his partnership with Evans, who he joined forces with on the same courts at the French Open earlier this year.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.999834768672374, \"rank\": 0.00016525863315581003, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he knows that the Olympics is a different beast when it comes to the doubles.\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray continued: \\\"But me and Evo have practised a bit together.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.49845743087573e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1756, \"end\": 1759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evolution_Championship_Series\", \"score\": 0.9999953127749707, \"rank\": 4.665201074267804e-06, \"text\": \"Evo\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evolution_Championship_Series\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evolution_Championship_Series\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have played tournaments together in the past.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have the potential to be a good team.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the Olympics doubles is different, because there is a lot of pairings in there, you know a lot of the singles guys are playing that maybe do not the rest of the year.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a lot of kind of scratch pairings.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But a lot of them can play extremely good tennis.\\\"\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Ex-Wimbledon champion confirms plan to retire at Olympics with Andy Murray  Do not miss:Rune joins Sinner in pulling out of 2024 Olympics tennis tournament with injury  Do not miss:John McEnroe's BBC wage and comparison to big earner Gary Lineker's salary  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.325022580819881e-60, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource