 in stone.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this week, he took to social media to confirm that the Olympics would be his last hurrah.\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Murray is at peace with his decision.\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2991, \"end\": 2997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.49845743087573e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy about it,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Look, a few months ago I did not know, I wasn't happy about potentially stopping, I was quite unsure about it.\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But now that the time is here, now I have made that decision definitively, I feel good about it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3410, \"end\": 3423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.112348102409382e-22, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3459, \"end\": 3472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.112348102409